<div class="span8 widget-span widget-type-cell main-content" style="" data-widget-type="cell" data-x="0" data-w="8">

<div class="row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 ">
<div class="row-fluid ">
<div class="span12 widget-span widget-type-widget_container " style="" data-widget-type="widget_container" data-x="0" data-w="12">
<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_1395325105318333" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget_container hs_cos_wrapper_type_widget_container" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget_container" data-hs-cos-type="widget_container"><div id="hs_cos_wrapper_widget_19107036902" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><h2>How to Find Product Documentation</h2>
<p>In an effort to ensure our customers always have the most updated product documentation, Semtech has improved the way documents are accessed on our website. The link which brought you to this page is no longer valid.</p>
<p>Documents are still available on our website. Here are few ways to find product documentation:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.semtech.com/search" rel=" noopener">Search by keyword, such as part number or brand name</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.semtech.com/design-support/product-guides" rel=" noopener">Filter all documents by product platform, product family and document category</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.semtech.com/products" rel=" noopener">Browse by Semtech product platform</a></li>
<li><a href="https://semtech.force.com/DP?__hstc=212684107.fb352f55728c903d4f39365f59ffa934.1558113816185.1571847660315.1571859514517.529&amp;__hssc=212684107.13.1571859514517&amp;__hsfp=1385406553" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Register for mySemtech to request access to private and confidential documents</a></li>
</ul></div></span>
</div><!--end widget-span -->
</div><!--end row-->
</div><!--end row-wrapper -->

</div><!--end widget-span -->
